---
const IG_URL = "https://www.instagram.com/nazbot.es/";
---

<section id="cta" class="section-py relative overflow-hidden bg-[#0f0f0f]">
  <div class="absolute inset-x-0 top-0 h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-white/8 to-transparent"></div>
  <div class="pointer-events-none absolute left-1/2 top-0 h-[500px] w-[700px] -translate-x-1/2 rounded-full opacity-8"
    style="background: radial-gradient(ellipse, rgba(79,158,255,0.06) 0%, transparent 65%);"></div>

  <div class="relative mx-auto max-w-2xl px-6 text-center lg:px-12">
    <div class="reveal">
      <span class="section-tag">Empieza hoy</span>
      <h2 class="mt-4 text-3xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-white sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl">
        Si hoy estás perdiendo leads
        <span class="gradient-text"> por falta de seguimiento, esto te interesa.</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="mx-auto mt-5 max-w-xl text-base leading-relaxed text-white/50">
        Nazbot instala un sistema claro para captar, responder y seguir mejor
        sin depender del caos diario. Un mensaje es suficiente para empezar.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-10 flex flex-col items-center gap-4 reveal delay-100">
      <a href={IG_URL} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn-accent text-base px-10 py-4">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
          <rect x="2" y="2" width="20" height="20" rx="5" ry="5"/>
          <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="4"/>
          <circle cx="17.5" cy="6.5" r="1" fill="currentColor" stroke="none"/>
        </svg>
        Escríbeme "SISTEMA" por DM
      </a>
      <a href="#demos" class="text-sm text-white/35 hover:text-white/60 transition-colors">
        Ver demo primero
      </a>
      <p class="text-xs text-white/25">Sin compromiso · Respondo en menos de 24h</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .section-py { padding-top: 7rem; padding-bottom: 7rem; }
</style>
